attributes.Long form description: The student is building a shelf. They start by inspecting the shelf pieces and assembling the legs. Next, they add the pipes and screw them into place. Then they add the trays and screw them into place. Finally, they add the wheels and screw them into place.

attributes.Transcription: All right. Now, we're looking at the IKEA furniture.
Please, assemble this shelf.
